#: .\templates\api\index.html:90
msgid "iPhone 17e"
msgstr "iPhone 17e"

#: .\templates\api\index.html:91
msgid ""
"iPhone 17e — Applening 2026-yilda taqdim etilgan “byudjet” modeli bo‘lib, u "
"6.1 dyuymli Super Retina XDR OLED displey, A19 chip va 48 MP kamera tizimi "
"bilan jihozlangan."
msgstr ""
"iPhone 17e — Apple’s budget model introduced in 2026, equipped with a "
"6.1‑inch Super Retina XDR OLED display, A19 chip, and a 48 MP camera system."

#: .\templates\api\index.html:104
msgid "iPhone 16"
msgstr "iPhone 16"

#: .\templates\api\index.html:105
msgid ""
"iPhone 16 — Apple’ning 2024-yilda taqdim etilgan flagman modeli bo‘lib, u "
"6.1 dyuymli Super Retina XDR OLED displey, A18 chip va 48 MP kamera tizimi "
"bilan jihozlangan."
msgstr ""
"iPhone 16 — Apple’s flagship model introduced in 2024, featuring a 6.1‑inch "
"Super Retina XDR OLED display, A18 chip, and a 48 MP camera system."

#: .\templates\api\index.html:118 .\templates\api\index.html:134
msgid "iPhone 17 Pro Max"
msgstr "iPhone 17 Pro Max"

#: .\templates\api\index.html:119
msgid ""
"iPhone 17 Pro Max — Applening eng so‘nggi flagman modeli bo‘lib, u 6.9 "
"dyuymli Super Retina XDR displey, A19 Pro chip va 48 MP kamera tizimi bilan "
"jihozlangan."
msgstr ""
"iPhone 17 Pro Max — Apple’s latest flagship model, equipped with a 6.9‑inch "
"Super Retina XDR display, A19 Pro chip, and a 48 MP camera system."

#: .\templates\api\index.html:135
msgid ""
"iPhone 17 Pro Max Silver — Applening eng so‘nggi flagman modeli bo‘lib, u "
"6.9 dyuymli Super Retina XDR displey, A19 Pro chip va 48 MP kamera tizimi "
"bilan jihozlangan. "
msgstr ""
"iPhone 17 Pro Max Silver — Apple’s latest flagship model, featuring a "
"6.9‑inch Super Retina XDR display, A19 Pro chip, and a 48 MP camera system."

#: .\templates\api\index.html:148
msgid "iPhone 14 Pro"
msgstr "iPhone 14 Pro"

#: .\templates\api\index.html:149
msgid ""
"iPhone 14 Pro — Applening 2022-yilda taqdim etilgan flagman modeli bo‘lib, u "
"6.1 dyuymli Super Retina XDR displey, A16 Bionic chip va 48 MP kamera tizimi "
"bilan jihozlangan."
msgstr ""
"iPhone 14 Pro — Apple’s flagship model introduced in 2022, equipped with a "
"6.1‑inch Super Retina XDR display, A16 Bionic chip, and a 48 MP camera "
"system."

#: .\templates\api\index.html:162
msgid "iPhone 15"
msgstr "iPhone 15"

#: .\templates\api\index.html:163
msgid ""
"iPhone 15 — Applening 2023-yilda taqdim etilgan flagman modeli bo‘lib, u 6.1 "
"dyuymli Super Retina XDR displey, A16 Bionic chip va 48 MP kamera tizimi "
"bilan jihozlangan."
msgstr ""
"iPhone 15 — Apple’s flagship model introduced in 2023, featuring a 6.1‑inch "
"Super Retina XDR display, A16 Bionic chip, and a 48 MP camera system."

