msgid "Bizning hamkorlar"
msgstr "Our partners"

#: .\templates\api\index.html:195
msgid "Samsung to'plamlari"
msgstr "Samsung kits"

#: .\templates\api\index.html:201
msgid "Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra"
msgstr "Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra"

#: .\templates\api\index.html:202
msgid ""
"Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra — Samsung’ning 2024-yilda taqdim etilgan flagman "
"modeli bo‘lib, u 6.8 dyuymli Dynamic AMOLED 2X displey, Snapdragon 8 Gen 3 "
"chip va 200 MP kamera tizimi bilan jihozlangan."
msgstr ""
"Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra — Samsung’s flagship model introduced in 2024, "
"equipped with a 6.8‑inch Dynamic AMOLED 2X display, Snapdragon 8 Gen 3 chip, "
"and a 200 MP camera system."

#: .\templates\api\index.html:215
msgid "Samsung Galaxy S26 Ultra"
msgstr "Samsung Galaxy S26 Ultra"

#: .\templates\api\index.html:216
msgid ""
"Samsung Galaxy S26 Ultra — Samsung’ning 2026-yilda taqdim etilgan eng kuchli "
"flagman modeli bo‘lib, u 6.9 dyuymli Dynamic AMOLED 2X displey, Snapdragon 8 "
"Elite Gen 5 chip va 200 MP asosiy kamera tizimi bilan jihozlangan."
msgstr ""
"Samsung Galaxy S26 Ultra — Samsung’s most powerful flagship model introduced "
"in 2026, featuring a 6.9‑inch Dynamic AMOLED 2X display, Snapdragon 8 Elite "
"Gen 5 chip, and a 200 MP main camera system."

#: .\templates\api\index.html:229
msgid "Samsung Galaxy A35"
msgstr "Samsung Galaxy A35"

#: .\templates\api\index.html:230
msgid ""
"Samsung Galaxy A35 — Samsung’ning 2024-yilda taqdim etilgan o‘rta narx "
"segmentidagi modeli bo‘lib, u 6.6 dyuymli Super AMOLED displey, Exynos 1380 "
"chip va 50 MP kamera tizimi bilan jihozlangan."
msgstr ""
"Samsung Galaxy A35 — Samsung’s mid‑range model introduced in 2024, equipped "
"with a 6.6‑inch Super AMOLED display, Exynos 1380 chip, and a 50 MP camera "
"system."

#: .\templates\api\index.html:243
msgid "Samsung Galaxy Z Fold"
msgstr "Samsung Galaxy Z Fold"

#: .\templates\api\index.html:244
msgid ""
"Samsung Galaxy Z Fold — Samsung’ning bukiladigan ekranli flagman smartfonlar "
"seriyasi bo‘lib, u innovatsion dizayn va kuchli texnik imkoniyatlari bilan "
"ajralib turadi."
msgstr ""
"Samsung Galaxy Z Fold — Samsung’s foldable‑screen flagship smartphone "
"series, distinguished by its innovative design and powerful technical "
"capabilities."

#: .\templates\api\index.html:257
msgid "Samsung Galaxy S23"
msgstr "Samsung Galaxy S23"

#: .\templates\api\index.html:258
msgid ""
"Samsung Galaxy S23 — Samsung’ning 2023-yilda taqdim etilgan flagman modeli "
"bo‘lib, u 6.1 dyuymli Dynamic AMOLED 2X displey, Snapdragon 8 Gen 2 chip va "
"50 MP kamera tizimi bilan jihozlangan."
msgstr ""
"Samsung Galaxy S23 — Samsung’s flagship model introduced in 2023, featuring "
"a 6.1‑inch Dynamic AMOLED 2X display, Snapdragon 8 Gen 2 chip, and a 50 MP "
"camera system."

#: .\templates\api\index.html:272
msgid "Samsung Galaxy S26"
msgstr "Samsung Galaxy S26"

#: .\templates\api\index.html:273
msgid ""
"Samsung Galaxy S26 — Samsung’ning 2026-yilda taqdim etilgan yangi flagman "
"modeli bo‘lib, u 6.3 dyuymli AMOLED displey, Snapdragon 8 Elite Gen 5 chip "
"va Galaxy AI funksiyalari bilan jihozlangan."
msgstr ""
"Samsung Galaxy S26 — Samsung’s new flagship model introduced in 2026, "
"equipped with a 6.3‑inch AMOLED display, Snapdragon 8 Elite Gen 5 chip, and "
"Galaxy AI features."

